OL,3,CHealth minister to outline Children's
OL,4,CHospice funding options by end of week
OL,6,FThe Health Minister Robin Swann has
OL,7,Fasked his officials to engage with the
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland's Children Hospice to
OL,9,Ftry and "determine the best way
OL,10,Fforward" by the end of this week.
OL,12,FThe children's hospice has been facing
OL,13,Fsevere funding challenges, which are
OL,14,Fbeing further heightened by a
OL,15,Freduction in government financing.
OL,17,FMr Swann said in a statement that he
OL,18,Fhoped to reach this determination on
OL,19,Fby the end of the week.
