OL,4,CHospice funding options by end of week
OL,6,FHis statement said: "The department
OL,7,Frecognises the vital role of hospices
OL,8,Fand has consistently resourced them to
OL,9,Fhelp deliver the critical services
OL,10,Fthey provide.
OL,12,F"The minister has asked his officials
OL,13,Fto look urgently at the issues raised,
OL,14,Fto engage with the hospice and to
OL,15,Fprovide a clear evidence base so he
OL,16,Fcan determine the best way forward
OL,17,Fbefore the end of the week."
OL,19,FOn Tuesday, the Children's Hospice
OL,20,Fannounced a reduction in beds blaming
OL,21,Fa loss of government funding.
