OL,6,FThe Glengormley facility is a charity
OL,7,Fwhich provides specialist palliative
OL,8,Fcare for more than 350 babies,
OL,9,Fchildren and their families every
OL,10,Fyear.JIt is the only service of its
OL,11,Ftype in Northern Ireland, supporting
OL,12,Fbabies, children, and their families
OL,13,Fthrough a range of services, including
OL,14,Fantenatal support and supported short
OL,15,Fbreaks.JIt requires more than
OL,16,F#20million annually to provide its
OL,17,Fservices.
