OL,6,FThe charity said the reduction was
OL,7,F"deeply regrettable and may
OL,8,Fpotentially incur a decrease in staff
OL,9,Fnumbers and a new working model".
OL,11,FGrace Stewart, acting director of
OL,12,FChildren's Hospice, said she
OL,13,Fprofoundly regretted having to
OL,14,Fimplement any reduction in capacity
OL,15,Fbut the move would help ensure its
OL,16,Flong term stability.
